{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDU1Mzg4NDk0", "number": 18953, "title": "#18951 : When the root path (\"/\") is being requested for the System Hos\u2026", "bodyText": "\u2026t or any other Site, the API must return the internal /System folder instance. In specific circumstances, during the Reindex Process, the Folder Factory is failing to read the /System folder appropriately. By calling the findSystemFolder() method now, we're making sure that the API is either (1) retrieving de System Folder from cache or the DB, or (2) re-creating it in case it has been deleted somehow.", "createdAt": "2020-07-22T22:33:42Z", "url": "https://github.com/dotCMS/core/pull/18953", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "c82549d4158292ec1d13baa5d93caee9d822b4b0"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-08-20T17:02:10Z", "author": {"login": "jcastro-dotcms"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 8, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABc3ioXpgH2gAyNDU1Mzg4NDk0OjY1ZWU2NmRhMGVmYWM3ZDg5NTYxZjczZjcwM2EzZGViM2ZhMWM2NTQ=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdAkS0DAFqTQ3MTAzMjg5Nw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "65ee66da0efac7d89561f73f703a3deb3fa1c654", "author": {"user": {"login": "jcastro-dotcms", "name": "Jose Castro"}}, "url": "https://github.com/dotCMS/core/commit/65ee66da0efac7d89561f73f703a3deb3fa1c654", "committedDate": "2020-07-22T22:32:47Z", "message": "#18951 : When the root path (\"/\") is being request for the System Host or any other Site, the API must return the internal `/System folder` instance. In specific circumstances, during the Reindex Process, the Folder Factory is failing to read the `/System folder` appropriately. By calling the `findSystemFolder()` method now, we're making sure that the API is either (1) retrieving de System Folder from cache or the DB, or (2) re-creating it in case it has been deleted somehow."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestRevi